overview: This series is chock full of girls who never settle for average. Featured cover girl Kenzie Reeves is a petite blonde with big dreams. But was Kenzie dreaming when she climbed on that stranger last night, or is that her way of letting her boyfriend down gently? Marica Hase, Chloe Scott, and Tasha Reign round out our lineup of voracious girls taking all they can handle.
title: Ample 2
